 @{" object " Link "object"}  Define an object
 @{" rotate " Link "rotate"}  Set an objects rotation
 @{" scale " Link "scale"}  Resize an object
 @{" texture " Link "texture"}  Add texture to an object's surface
 @{" translate " Link "translate"}  Position an object
 @{" no_shadow " Link "no_shadow"}  Make an object transparent
