     turbulence
     ----------
     Syntax: texture {
                ...
                turbulence #
             }
     
     Description: turbulence will distort a pattern so that it is not so "perfect".
                  Typcical values for turbulence range between 0.0 and 1.0, but
                  any value can be used.


@EndNode

